This app is for demonstration purposes only. Its functionality has been merged 
with Signature Capture app that you can download from here:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=biz.binarysolutions.signature

This app has been released under Apache License 2.0 and it's source code is
available here:
https://github.com/vbresan/signature-share

Report all issues here:
https://github.com/vbresan/signature-share/issues


Capture and share electronic signatures.
Sign by touching the screen.
Press and hold for context menu ('View', 'Share', 'Rename', 'Delete').

Depends on digital signature capture library. You will be prompted for it's
installation later on.

For other commercial purposes (like signing PDF documents etc.) contact
support e-mail.
